project_descr: Azerbaijan 2010 National Human Development Report on Civil Service Reform

outputs.output_descr:
Following outputs are considered to be achieved by the project:
Output Formulation  4 chapters of National Human Development Report, recommendations and statistical analysis and tables drafted by local experts; 
Output 2 Data collection  2 surveys conducted by local research company on image of civil service among civil servants, citizen and students in Baku and regions. 
Output 3 Publication and Presentation of the National Human Development Report
